      <data key="d0">Comparison of Convolutional Layer Configurations (text)</data>
      <data key="d1">text</data>
      <data key="d2">This content evaluates the benefits of using stacked smaller convolutional layers over a single large layer, highlighting enhanced non-linearity and reduced parameter count, essential for optimizing neural network architectures.</data>
