      <data key="d1">text</data>
      <data key="d2">This text discusses the role of $1 \times 1$ convolution layers in enhancing the nonlinearity of decision functions in neural networks, emphasizing their function as linear projections and their integration into advanced architectures like Network in Network.</data>
