      <data key="d1">table</data>
      <data key="d2">This table summarizes error rates of various Combined ConvNet models for the ILSVRC competition, revealing that post-submission strategies significantly reduce top-1 and top-5 validation errors, showcasing the effectiveness of multilayer processing and evaluation techniques.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-978a7e2e478746fb8097d20c2ae24e6a</data>
      <data key="d4">Very_Deep_Convolutional_Networks_for_Large-Scale_Image_Recognition_content_list.json</data>
