      <data key="d0">Ensemble Model Performance Analysis (text)</data>
      <data key="d1">text</data>
      <data key="d2">This text analyzes the performance of ensemble models by reporting a reduction in test error rates from 7.3% with 7 models to 6.8% with 2 models, highlighting the efficiency of model selection.</data>
