      <data key="d0">ILSVRC Classification Comparison (table)</data>
      <data key="d1">table</data>
      <data key="d2">This table compares classification errors across several methods in the ILSVRC challenge. VGG architectures demonstrate superior performance, particularly with ensemble approaches, while other models like GoogLeNet and MSRA show varied effectiveness, emphasizing the benefits of multi-network configurations.</data>
