      <data key="d0">ILSVRC Challenge Analysis (text)</data>
      <data key="d1">text</data>
      <data key="d2">This paper analyzes the localisation task of the ILSVRC challenge, detailing ConvNet architectures and methods employed, which won the challenge in 2014, while referencing prior work by Sermanet et al. The content transitions from classification to localisation with a focus on evaluation and methodology.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-141ed6c39acd3afb13737718c69bb057</data>
