      <data key="d1">text</data>
      <data key="d2">This section introduces the concept of localization within convolutional networks, highlighting its importance in processing spatial data. It serves as a foundational element for understanding subsequent discussions in the document.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-08168e749564023f1295b5d02c61d759</data>
      <data key="d4">Very_Deep_Convolutional_Networks_for_Large-Scale_Image_Recognition_content_list.json</data>
