      <data key="d0">Object Localization using ConvNet (text)</data>
      <data key="d1">text</data>
      <data key="d2">This text explains the use of a deep ConvNet for object localization, detailing how bounding box predictions are made through different regression techniques and highlighting the architecture that performs best in classification tasks.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-7b214b117388366f5c44206b6df45239</data>
      <data key="d4">Very_Deep_Convolutional_Networks_for_Large-Scale_Image_Recognition_content_list.json</data>
