      <data key="d1">text</data>
      <data key="d2">This content outlines the training methodology for localisation ConvNets, focusing on differences from classification ConvNets, training scales, fine-tuning strategies, and initialisation methods applied in the context of ILSVRC-2014.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-5af3169afc1b617a801c2fc164adace2</data>
      <data key="d4">Very_Deep_Convolutional_Networks_for_Large-Scale_Image_Recognition_content_list.json</data>
