      <data key="d2">This text explores the application of deep learning models as feature extractors on smaller datasets, highlights their performance advantages over shallow models, and discusses transfer learning's impact, referencing key studies in the field.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-75d1f552a2805d55c662bc781d1dfbb2</data>
