      <data key="d1">text</data>
      <data key="d2">The content outlines a methodology for using pre-trained ConvNets on ILSVRC for image classification on new datasets by adapting network architecture, extracting features, and utilizing linear SVM classifiers without fine-tuning pre-trained weights.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-5619adfb7559b7fa15655e31d05a6f68</data>
