      <data key="d1">text</data>
      <data key="d2">This text discusses the methodology for aggregating image features using a procedure similar to an ILSVRC evaluation, detailing image rescaling, descriptor averaging, and multi-scale feature extraction, and assessing the implications of stacking versus pooling features in network evaluations.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-0b3792d8c58c852355ce9d281a964822</data>
