      <data key="d1">text</data>
      <data key="d2">This text outlines the evaluation of image classification tasks using PASCAL VOC-2007 and VOC-2012 datasets, focusing on dataset specifics, image annotations, data accessibility, and the evaluation metric, mean average precision (mAP).</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-cd2cd03b37de5645b6e6c7e95af46e46</data>
