      <data key="d0">Aggregation of Image Descriptors in VOC Dataset (text)</data>
      <data key="d1">text</data>
      <data key="d2">This text analyzes the efficacy of averaging image descriptors across various scales in the VOC dataset, noting the challenges posed by scale diversity and the marginal benefits observed from a limited range of scales. It highlights the importance of dimensionality management in enhancing classifier performance.</data>
