      <data key="d5">1774858926</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Caltech-256">
      <data key="d0">Caltech-256</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">A large-scale object category dataset developed at Caltech, used for image recognition benchmarking.&lt;SEP&gt;Caltech-256 is a dataset used for evaluating mean class recall in image classification.&lt;SEP&gt;Caltech-256 is a larger dataset with 31,000 images spanning 257 classes, used for image classification benchmarking.&lt;SEP&gt;Caltech-256 is a dataset used to assess the features of neural network models, with Net-E outperforming previous state-of-the-art methods.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-40bfade9d2720e8c40f7ccada6980ef7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-18ada958b761b3b461355a37d487ef5d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1f5bdd5865b487e29cc5aa8228165cc7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4bd2f337bd598e8c48e820585a63127d</data>
