    <node id="Validation Set">
      <data key="d0">Validation Set</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">Part of the ILSVRC-2012 dataset with 50,000 images used to validate models during training.&lt;SEP&gt;The validation set is used as a test set during experiments to evaluate the performance of image classification models.&lt;SEP&gt;The validation set was used to measure the model's top-1 and top-5 error rates with best configurations.&lt;SEP&gt;The validation set is used in the first testing protocol to evaluate and compare network modifications.</data>
