    <node id="Top-1 Error">
      <data key="d0">Top-1 Error</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">A performance metric in image classification indicating the proportion of images incorrectly classified as the top prediction.&lt;SEP&gt;Top-1 error rate measured on the validation set, indicating the model's accuracy in predicting the correct class.</data>
