    <node id="Top-5 Error">
      <data key="d0">Top-5 Error</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">A performance metric indicating the proportion of images where the correct label is not among the top five predicted labels.&lt;SEP&gt;Top-5 error rate indicating the frequency the true class is outside the top five predictions, with specific value achieved by configuration E.</data>
