      <data key="d2">ICLR 2015 is the conference where the paper was published, situated within a specific event and timeframe.&lt;SEP&gt;The International Conference on Learning Representations (ICLR) held in 2015 is an academic conference where research papers are presented.&lt;SEP&gt;ICLR 2015 is an academic conference focused on machine learning and deep learning, where the paper was presented.&lt;SEP&gt;ICLR 2015 is the specific instance of the conference where the work was published.&lt;SEP&gt;ICLR 2015 is an international conference on learning representations where academic papers are presented.</data>
