    <node id="VOC-2007">
      <data key="d0">VOC-2007</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">VOC-2007 is a dataset used to evaluate image classification performance, with mean AP scores reported for different methods.&lt;SEP&gt;VOC-2007 is a dataset used for image classification benchmarks with approximately 10,000 images annotated with labels across 20 object categories.&lt;SEP&gt;VOC-2007 is a dataset used for validation in image descriptor performance analysis.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-cd2cd03b37de5645b6e6c7e95af46e46&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-13c671232831711c90250ba5e0433558&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1f5bdd5865b487e29cc5aa8228165cc7</data>
