    <node id="2015">
      <data key="d0">2015</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">The entity "2015" refers to the year in which a conference paper was both published and presented at the International Conference on Learning Representations (ICLR). Multiple descriptions confirm that 2015 marks the publication date, providing a crucial temporal context for the research documented in the paper. Additionally, several descriptions specify that 2015 is the year the paper was presented at ICLR, emphasizing its role in the dissemination of the research findings during that year. Combined, these descriptions indicate that 2015 is significant as both the publication and presentation year for the conference paper associated with ICLR, establishing the temporal frame within which the research was made publicly accessible and discussed within the academic community.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-ea3c4d36ff2b24508dbc837273429e62&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3900af70e9c2fbecc4412901ec29ab8a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-af1ec995fccd39dcbc23bdfc756e4874&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1484bff7de9771e89c43e73466a0166e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6b3b56ce2f3d33421ac0bd9c6ed9d458&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-582a39d261b96a9d696665560af28e80&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8bef79dc2ff396e9081fcf89d7023bfe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f3e9154cc1f602f38606d057becb87cb</data>
