    <node id="Object">
      <data key="d0">Object</data>
      <data key="d1">smallobject</data>
      <data key="d2">A small object or object part can be contained within a crop of the image when 'S' is large.&lt;SEP&gt;Objects in Caltech images typically occupy the entire image frame, representing whole objects or parts.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-a661234bc5d404231fbf23c25c0f103e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-910b19d5d7e003782ec85519b01d0c2b</data>
