      <data key="d0">Whole-Image Statistics</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">Whole-image statistics refer to the comprehensive information derived from the entire training image, captured when 'S' is equal to the crop size.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-a661234bc5d404231fbf23c25c0f103e</data>
