      <data key="d1">organization</data>
      <data key="d2">Szegedy et al. (2014) is a referenced neural network model that is used as a performance benchmark for comparison against the author's model.&lt;SEP&gt;Researchers cited for their crop evaluation methodology involving 144 crops over 4 scales.</data>
