      <data key="d0">Weight Layers</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">The neural network architecture features 22 weight layers contributing to its depth and complexity.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-ec1e400414ae226381210995dc5442d4</data>
