      <data key="d5">1774858994</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Configuration D">
      <data key="d0">Configuration D</data>
      <data key="d1">configuration</data>
      <data key="d2">Configuration D is a ConvNet with 19 layers, employing $3 \\times 3$ conv. layers throughout the network, performing better than configuration C.&lt;SEP&gt;Configuration D is a deep neural network configuration that performs well in the study.&lt;SEP&gt;Configuration D is a specific model setup tested with different evaluation techniques and associated error rates in the table.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-7bd4c026d1ee9227f8df517ef0dc9a7a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bbd329f6e34d77e2545b8b6ff2369cfd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b7e76372644452c1c01e819997c40c4c</data>
