    <node id="Shallow Net">
      <data key="d0">Shallow Net</data>
      <data key="d1">content</data>
      <data key="d2">A shallow neural network has fewer layers and parameters compared to deeper models, with larger convolutional layers.&lt;SEP&gt;A shallow network with five $5 \\times 5$ conv. layers, derived from configuration B by replacing pairs of $3 \\times 3$ conv. layers.&lt;SEP&gt;A simpler neural network model used as a benchmark comparison in experiments.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-d6f4d23968c5e45cadd7773c219289a0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-45781abc0aae16aa276329cd21266d04&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b7e76372644452c1c01e819997c40c4c</data>
