    <node id="Deep Neural Network">
      <data key="d0">Deep Neural Network</data>
      <data key="d1">content</data>
      <data key="d2">Deep neural networks are architectures characterized by multiple convolutional layers, with their depth being a key aspect analyzed for performance improvements.&lt;SEP&gt;A neural network with a large depth, involving multiple layers, influencing parameter counts.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-d6f4d23968c5e45cadd7773c219289a0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-668a86d65078bf8021d84fd665b305f7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1f5bdd5865b487e29cc5aa8228165cc7</data>
