    <node id="Evaluation Method">
      <data key="d0">Evaluation Method</data>
      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">Evaluation methods such as dense, multi-crop, and multi-crop &amp; dense are techniques used to assess the performance of ConvNet configurations.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-bbd329f6e34d77e2545b8b6ff2369cfd</data>
      <data key="d4">Very_Deep_Convolutional_Networks_for_Large-Scale_Image_Recognition_content_list.json</data>
