    </node>
    <node id="ILSVRC">
      <data key="d0">ILSVRC</data>
      <data key="d1">event</data>
      <data key="d2">The ImageNet Large-Scale Visual Recognition Challenge (ILSVRC) is a highly influential annual competition and benchmark in the field of computer vision, primarily focused on image classification, localization, and object detection. It serves as a standard platform for evaluating the performance of various image recognition models, including neural networks such as convolutional neural networks (ConvNets). The challenge involves providing a dataset and a series of tasks where participating models are trained and subsequently tested on their ability to accurately categorize and localize objects within images.

ILSVRC plays a crucial role in fostering advancements in image recognition technology by encouraging the development and comparison of sophisticated algorithms. It is widely referenced in research papers and has significantly contributed to the progress of deep learning approaches in computer vision. The challenge is conducted annually, with top-performing models submitted and evaluated based on their accuracy in classification and localization tasks. Overall, ILSVRC is regarded as a key benchmark and dataset that supports the evaluation and improvement of machine learning models in the domain of image recognition.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-cb0d159c3ed83612608daea64febc962&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9bd30b9c62f11080adc575b0dedc0a8f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-47b4639bc17afbd91af6777585180e5b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-45781abc0aae16aa276329cd21266d04&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d9cbdf6566eaa98874d4dcfde2604ba8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e9715bf667856c07b75fd472ffa9d1aa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-75d1f552a2805d55c662bc781d1dfbb2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-875f06379a938719e62d111c5e539876&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5619adfb7559b7fa15655e31d05a6f68&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-14272cd8cfed2559a0d49d220903d49c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b57396de46bdf86a2f9a27a50e7e4731&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-45b8e81b5253dda8099181146e449c4b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-185820c0acd5f2e9b1560edd052c7535&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-57f210dde350132bd52b55e78346cd16</data>
      <data key="d4">Very_Deep_Convolutional_Networks_for_Large-Scale_Image_Recognition_content_list.json</data>
      <data key="d5">1774858997</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
