      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">Evaluation techniques such as dense, multi-crop, and multi-crop &amp; dense are methods used to assess ConvNet performance.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-bbd329f6e34d77e2545b8b6ff2369cfd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-755c65f8601f3609b280a7759369f207</data>
