    <node id="Goodfellow">
      <data key="d0">Goodfellow</data>
      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Goodfellow et al. (2014) are researchers who applied deep convolutional neural networks with 11 weight layers to street number recognition.</data>
