      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">A process where a convolutional network evaluates an entire image without cropping, utilizing padding from neighboring parts.&lt;SEP&gt;Dense evaluation is an evaluation technique where dense cropping and testing are used to assess model performance.&lt;SEP&gt;Dense evaluation refers to analyzing images with comprehensive or overlapping regions to refine model predictions.</data>
