    <node id="Object Recognition">
      <data key="d0">Object Recognition</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Object recognition refers to the process where the model identifies objects in images, capable of recognizing objects at different scales.&lt;SEP&gt;Object recognition involves identifying and classifying objects within images, and the text discusses a specific approach in this domain.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-ee7c860b03e66807d924aa12f0a62399&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6247855fe0930ba59c41d64d91122ec1</data>
      <data key="d4">Very_Deep_Convolutional_Networks_for_Large-Scale_Image_Recognition_content_list.json</data>
      <data key="d5">1774859003</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Multi-Scale Model">
      <data key="d0">Multi-Scale Model</data>
      <data key="d1">content</data>
      <data key="d2">A multi-scale model is trained to recognize objects over a wide range of sizes, leveraging multiple scales to improve accuracy.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-ee7c860b03e66807d924aa12f0a62399</data>
      <data key="d4">Very_Deep_Convolutional_Networks_for_Large-Scale_Image_Recognition_content_list.json</data>
      <data key="d5">1774859003</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Single-Scale Model">
      <data key="d0">Single-Scale Model</data>
      <data key="d1">content</data>
      <data key="d2">A single-scale model is used as a basis for training the multi-scale model by fine-tuning its layers.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-ee7c860b03e66807d924aa12f0a62399</data>
      <data key="d4">Very_Deep_Convolutional_Networks_for_Large-Scale_Image_Recognition_content_list.json</data>
      <data key="d5">1774859003</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Fine-Tuning">
      <data key="d0">Fine-Tuning</data>
      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">Fine-tuning involves adjusting all layers of a model pre-trained with fixed parameters to improve performance on a specific task.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-ee7c860b03e66807d924aa12f0a62399</data>
      <data key="d4">Very_Deep_Convolutional_Networks_for_Large-Scale_Image_Recognition_content_list.json</data>
      <data key="d5">1774859003</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
