      <data key="d2">Table 9 displays the results of applying the localisation ConvNet to the whole image, showing improvement over previous methods.&lt;SEP&gt;Table 9 is a data presentation titled 'Localisation error' that displays various localisation error percentages related to different image sizes during training and testing phases.</data>
