      <data key="d3">chunk-9adb23bad920b5e09b440160ad210992</data>
      <data key="d2">Aggregating descriptors over a range of scales including {2, 5, 6, 3, 8, 4, 5, 1, 2, 6, 4, 0, 7, 6, 8} yields only marginal performance gains (~0.3%) beyond smaller subsets.</data>
      <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
