    <edge source="Net-E" target="Net-D">
      <data key="d7">2.0</data>
      <data key="d8">Net-D and Net-E are compared based on their classification performance.&lt;SEP&gt;Net-E performs better than Net-D, and their combination further improves the performance.</data>
