    <edge source="Net-E" target="Chatfield et al. (2014)">
      <data key="d7">1.0</data>
      <data key="d8">Net-E surpasses the previous state-of-the-art approach of Chatfield et al. (2014) on Caltech-256 by 8.6%.</data>
